caption.title: Retraction dynamics and expansion of the distribution area of Ceratophrys cranwelli, according to the niche modeling method.
caption.p: Last interglacial (A); Last glacial maximum (B) and Current (C). (A): 67,880 km 2; (B): 82,321 km 2 and (C): 69,362 km 2. Training data: AUC = 0.966 (A); AUC = 0.950 (B) and AUC = 0.956 (C). Test data: AUC = 0.930 (A); AUC = 0.942 (B) and AUC = 0.942 (C).
